- cs.OH (Other Computer Science): This category is for papers that do not fit into any other category. While the paper is related to networking and signal processing, it may not fit neatly into any specific sub-category.
- cs.PF (Performance): The paper discusses techniques for improving the performance of optical communication systems, which could fall under the performance sub-category.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages): This category is unlikely to be relevant to the paper, as it does not appear to discuss programming languages or related topics.
